properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 14 at 3:35AM EST until February 15 at 6:00PM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Highest gusts up to 45 kt and highest waves around 12
feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 6 PM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous highest waves which
could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 6 PM EST SATURDAY
